<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.212632>
    dc:description "FIGURES 20 – 24. Male genitalia of Eudonia spp. 20. E. hexamera sp. n., holotype, genitalia slide No. LWC 08224; 21. E. magna sp. n., holotype, genitalia slide No. LWC 07476; 22, E. duospinata sp. n., holotype, genitalia slide No. LWC 06212; 23. E. cavata sp. n., holotype, genitalia slide No. LWC 05025; 24. E. tibetalis (Caradja), genitalia slide No. LWC 08110 (scales: 0.5 mm)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/212632/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.212635>
    dc:description "FIGURES 31 – 34. Female genitalia of Eudonia spp. 31. E. hexamera sp. n., paratype, genitalia slide No. LWC 06257; 32. E. magna sp. n., paratype, genitalia slide No. LWC 08010; 33. E. duospinata sp. n., paratype, genitalia slide No. LWC 07505; 34. E. cavata sp. n., paratype, genitalia slide No. LWC 08073 (scales: 0.5 mm)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/212635/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.212631>
    dc:description "FIGURES 14 – 19. Male genitalia of Eudonia spp. 14. E. singulannulata sp. n., holotype, genitalia slide No. LWC 06272; 15. E. rectilineata sp. n., holotype, genitalia slide No. LWC 08058; 16. E. wolongensis sp. n., holotype, genitalia slide No. LWC 08047; 17. E. lijiangensis sp. n., holotype, genitalia slide No. LWC 08128; 18. E. zhongdianensis sp. n., holotype, genitalia slide No. LWC 06002; 19. E. furva sp. n., holotype, genitalia slide No. LWC 06135 (scales: 0.5 mm)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/212631/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.212633>
    dc:description "FIGURES 25 – 27. Female genitalia of Eudonia spp. 25. E. singulannulata sp. n., paratype, genitalia slide No. LWC 07499; 26. E. rectilineata sp. n., paratype, genitalia slide No. LWC 08244; 27. E. wolongensis sp. n., paratype, genitalia slide No. LWC 08074 (scales: 0.5 mm)." ;
